OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,FJersey Bulls Women thrashed their
OL,7,Fopponents Milford and Witley in the
OL,8,Flast game of the season, securing the
OL,9,Ftitle and concluding their perfect
OL,10,Fseason.
OL,12,FIts the women's first ever season in
OL,13,FEnglish League football, and they won
OL,14,Fall 17 games they played in South East
OL,15,FCounties Women 's Football League
OL,16,FSurrey Division One.
OL,18,FThere was an 18th, which they were
OL,19,Fwinning when it was voided.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,FThe team who've finished top of the
OL,7,Ftable, hope they can can be promoted
OL,8,Fby more than one level next season.
OL,10,FManager Chad Morris said their success
OL,11,Fhas been 'unreal'.
OL,13,F"It's all credit to the players. They
OL,14,Fcould when they were told they had won
OL,15,Fthe league the other night, not turned
OL,16,Fup, and not put a shift in, but as per
OL,17,Fnormal, I think that second half they
OL,18,Fblue them out of the water."
OL,20,FHe added it's been a great season, but
OL,21,Fthe women have had to be committed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,F"It's easy saying that when its June,
OL,7,Fand like today the weather is nice,
OL,8,Fand you're standing here in your
OL,9,Fshorts.
OL,11,F"It's a different matter at half four
OL,12,Fin January, when you're having to get
OL,13,Fup, fly, go to a ground that maybe
OL,14,Fisn't the best, when it's pouring with
OL,15,Frain and then play, and then do that
OL,16,Fevery other week. So their commitment
OL,17,Fhas been unreal."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
