OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,FChad said the idea behind the team was
OL,7,Ftwo fold: "It was to give the better
OL,8,Fplayers in the island an opportunity,
OL,9,Fbut also for the younger girls. As
OL,10,Fyou've seen here today, we've had
OL,11,Fd'Auvergne school here as mascots, all
OL,12,Fwanting the team's autographs at the
OL,13,Fend, so they become role models
OL,14,Fimmediately."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
