OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,FPlayer Lauren Queree said: "It's hard
OL,7,Fto put the feeling into words. We've
OL,8,Fbeen waiting for the Bulls and this
OL,9,Fkind of thing to happen for such a
OL,10,Flong time. So for it to happen and for
OL,11,Fus to do the unbeaten and to win 100%
OL,12,Fof the games is just absolutely
OL,13,Famazing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
