PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1777558268
OL,3,CJersey Bulls women win league and
OL,4,Csecure promotion
OL,6,FRoisin Flynn who scored five goals
OL,7,Fagainst Milford and Witley added:
OL,8,F"It's been amazing. With Jersey going
OL,9,Fto the Island Games and the Muratti,
OL,10,Fthe big games, it's so nice to have it
OL,11,Fall year round, and we're not waiting
OL,12,Ffor the next big thing. So it's been a
OL,13,Fgreat opportunity for us."
OL,15,FShe added: The relationships between
OL,16,Fus have got so close, we know
OL,17,Feveryone's strengths and weaknesses."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
